Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:27.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:31.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}即使如此 go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}咬紧牙关 became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}连有眼泪都宛如灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:41.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}一个sign 一个light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:47.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿没有黎明的夜晚 歌声不会间断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:52.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿不要困在和彷徨迷惑的梦境里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:58.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿交错的足迹们不再执着过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:05.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿就算你一旦失足 也千万别放手
