Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:17.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿能勇敢面对没有结束的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:23.50,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 生命的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:30.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}还在发出声响 与你一起
